{"id": 961, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在网上买东西时要怎么做才能感到安心？", "description": "有时候显得多此一举，但为了安心也必须要再三确认。（题图来自：Helena Perez Gracia）", "record_count": 3640, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703130108JuSPfpRZjizeKb1U.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-07-04T03:06:00Z", "options": [{"id": 95232, "content": "很大可能上会去旗舰店", "image": null, "praise_count": 322, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115462}, {"id": 95233, "content": "会把店铺放到微博搜一下评价", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 484896}, {"id": 95234, "content": "如果全是好评没有中差评就感觉这家店一定是刷的。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 298, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 666486}, {"id": 95235, "content": "足够便宜以至于扔了也不心疼", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 363108}, {"id": 104195, "content": "买家秀，细节图", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700756}, {"id": 95236, "content": "看差评，看追加", "image": null, "praise_count": 567, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 400105}, {"id": 95237, "content": "和客服反复确认，让ta以性命担保。", "image": null, "praise_count": 100, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179207}, {"id": 95238, "content": "觉得除非是旗舰店、熟悉的代购店，或者是小作坊的定制货，一般不会轻易在网上买东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 662237}, {"id": 95239, "content": "旗舰店也有假货啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 620705}, {"id": 95240, "content": "排在第一的一定不买", "image": null, "praise_count": 93, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423267}, {"id": 97544, "content": "看差评，晒图，自己拿卷尺量尺寸和尺寸表作对比，问客服。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 677660}, {"id": 95241, "content": "把整个淘宝的同款看一遍，全部。嗯。", "image": null, "praise_count": 69, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 429917}, {"id": 95242, "content": "必须把店铺里所有商品翻到底…", "image": null, "praise_count": 159, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 441985}, {"id": 95243, "content": "看买家有图评价", "image": null, "praise_count": 72, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 666509}, {"id": 99339, "content": "看店家的等级", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 681377}, {"id": 95244, "content": "看中差评，看追加，看晒单，看店铺格调", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 563497}, {"id": 95245, "content": "货比三家", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 666515}, {"id": 95246, "content": "必看评论", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 663495}, {"id": 95247, "content": "无图无真相", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 571608}, {"id": 95248, "content": "销量、差评和买家秀", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 522720}, {"id": 95249, "content": "信任买过的店铺放首位，如果在天猫买 会选择旗舰店 如果同款商品有好几家店铺会反复对比评价价格等再下单 还是不太心安 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654055}, {"id": 95250, "content": "运费险！", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 666523}, {"id": 95251, "content": "必须要看到带图买家秀，且有中肯的评价。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643918}, {"id": 95253, "content": "留言：请在发货前检查质量尺码颜色，不接受任何瑕疵。谢谢。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 595556}, {"id": 104469, "content": "每个链接点进去都要对比价格，因为可以多个规格在一个商品链接，搜索结果的时候淘宝只显示最低的一个，奸商都把一个链接的商品设置了多个规格，里面有个低的价格去争搜索结果排前面，点进去发现要买的东西贵的要死！真是浪费时间。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 2337}, {"id": 95254, "content": "看评价，一直不停的翻看评价，有差评的一般不会买", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649889}, {"id": 95255, "content": "看评论，好评中评差评图片追平一个不放过，看完默默的关掉网页，安心了", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 666542}, {"id": 95256, "content": "看图说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 96794}, {"id": 95257, "content": "旗舰店 看图看差评看追加", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643161}, {"id": 95258, "content": "旗舰店?", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 666579}, {"id": 95259, "content": "商品实物图   中差评   店铺信誉   还有客服的态度……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 665783}, {"id": 95260, "content": "买两个码，退一个", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 589115}, {"id": 95261, "content": "看总销量  除了衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 655100}, {"id": 95517, "content": "朋友介绍", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668232}, {"id": 95262, "content": "大发", "image": "img/option/option/20160704124543HfXU497MPRmBESQz.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 600435}, {"id": 95263, "content": "就算写着自由下单，也要联系一下客服", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 538436}, {"id": 97824, "content": "差评是真话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 663476}, {"id": 95265, "content": "七天无理由退换货", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114719}, {"id": 97825, "content": "只上官网", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 663476}, {"id": 95266, "content": "七天无理由退换货", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664125}, {"id": 95267, "content": "看差评", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 666617}, {"id": 95268, "content": "看图 看差评 货比三家", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 427991}, {"id": 95269, "content": "买运费险", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118131}, {"id": 98341, "content": "七天无条件退换", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680452}, {"id": 95270, "content": "必须看买家秀图", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 579627}, {"id": 95271, "content": "能看的评价都看一遍?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 626900}, {"id": 95272, "content": "看带图评论和差评，还有有问必答～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 614327}, {"id": 95275, "content": "货比三家", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 666650}, {"id": 95276, "content": "看老婆脸色", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 656256}, {"id": 96044, "content": "带 韩版  爆款  欧洲站  森系全部略过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419378}]}